name: Poo Pup Club 2021
description: Join the gang as they create their world in Poo Pup land! Kit Kat club was formed and now the pups are out to get them. I have been drawing these since I was 6 years old and put them away for years. Now they are back from the dead to make you smile with craziness. Who will win this battle of cuteness and grossness????
